    <element name="Path of Mutation" type="Archetype" source="Kibbles' Compendium of Legends and Legacies" id="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION">
        <supports>Primal Path</supports>
        <description>
            <p>For most Barbarians, their rage manifests as a mystically empowered state of mind, but Barbarians of this path manifest their rage in a more profound and physical manner. Barbarians of the Path of Mutation embody their rage through terrifying mutation, transforming into hulking brutes.</p>
            <p class="indent">The origin of their power varies, be it ancient blood awakening, consumption of an alchemical substance, blessing of astral entities, or a past exposure to specific kinds of radiant damage. Regardless, the effects all embody physical manifestation of a Barbarians rage, granting them increased power, size, and durability. The form these manifestations take varies for each barbarian; some grow into towering monstrous humanoids, some take on draconic aspects, some channel their powers to become giant apes or other beasts, while others simply turn large and green.</p>
            <div element="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_TRANSFORMING_RAGE" />
            <div element="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_COLLATERAL_DAMAGE" />
            <div element="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_ADAPTIVE_RAGE" />
            <div element="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_BUILDING_FRUSTRATION" />
            <div element="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_HULKING_SMASH" />
        </description>
        <sheet display="false">
            <description></description>
        </sheet>
        <rules>
            <grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_TRANSFORMING_RAGE" level="3" />
            <grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_COLLATERAL_DAMAGE" level="3" />
            <grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_KTH_COLAL_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_BARBARIAN_MUTATION_ADAPTIVE_RAGE" level="6" />
